    <h2>Quick Bog Facts</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>They are important carbon sinks.</li>
      <li>Home to unique and often endangered species.</li>
      <li>Threatened by activities like drainage for agriculture, peat extraction, and climate change.</li>
      <li>Known for preserving ancient artifacts in their peat, including remarkably well-preserved bodies known as bog bodies.</li>
    </ul>
